Chelsea's shock collapse to a 5-2 defeat with 10 men against West Brom helped Liverpool's cause to close the gap between the two sides to just two pointsSpurs' latest failure to hold onto a lead at St James' Park will do little to quell the speculation over Harry Kane's futureFulham collapsed to concede three times in the final 12 minutes at Villa Park and left their manager bemoaning a lack of experience